name: FinanceTest
description: Test suite for validating various financial data generation functionalities provided by the Finance class.

test_cases.name: creditCard
test_cases.description: Tests the generation of a credit card number and validates it using the Luhn algorithm.

test_cases.name: nasdaqTicker
test_cases.description: Tests the generation of a NASDAQ ticker symbol and validates its format.

test_cases.name: nyseTicker
test_cases.description: Tests the generation of a NYSE ticker symbol and validates its format.

test_cases.name: bic
test_cases.description: Tests the generation of a BIC (Bank Identifier Code) and validates its format.

test_cases.name: iban
test_cases.description: Tests the generation of an IBAN (International Bank Account Number) and validates its format.

test_cases.name: ibanWithCountryCode
test_cases.description: Tests the generation of an IBAN with a specific country code and validates its format.

test_cases.name: ibanCountryCodes
test_cases.description: Tests the retrieval of supported IBAN country codes and ensures the list is not empty.

test_cases.name: ibanWithAllCountryCodes
test_cases.description: Tests the generation of IBANs for all supported country codes and ensures each IBAN is not blank.

test_cases.name: creditCardWithType
test_cases.description: Tests the generation of credit card numbers for all supported types and validates them using the Luhn algorithm.

test_cases.name: costaRicaIbanMustBeValid
test_cases.description: Tests the generation of an IBAN for Costa Rica and validates it using the Iban class.

test_cases.name: visaCard
test_cases.description: Tests the generation of a Visa credit card number and validates its format.

test_cases.name: discoverCard
test_cases.description: Tests the generation of a Discover credit card number and validates its format.

test_cases.name: usRoutingNumber
test_cases.description: Tests the generation of a US routing number and validates its format and checksum.
